<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:15:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>塞尔维亚议会批准联合政府</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-parliament-approves-coalition-government-2024-05-02/</link><description>塞尔维亚议会周四批准了一个联合政府，新当选的总理米洛斯·武切维奇将其描述为“连续性政府”，它将带领巴尔干国家应对地缘政治挑战以及与科索沃的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-parliament-approves-coalition-government-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称有关其与朝鲜军事关系的说法不准确</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-calls-claim-about-its-alleged-military-ties-with-north-korea-inaccurate-2024-05-02/</link><description>俄罗斯周四表示，西方关于其与朝鲜进行军事合作的说法是不准确的，并表示其与平壤的关系既不针对第三国，也不威胁该地区的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-calls-claim-about-its-alleged-military-ties-with-north-korea-inaccurate-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国孖士打律师事务所将退出香港合伙企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-law-firm-mayer-brown-split-hong-kong-partnership-2024-05-02/</link><description>美国孖士打律师事务所周四表示，由于许多国际律师事务所重新考虑或减少在中国的业务，该公司计划从目前的香港业务中分离出来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 14:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-law-firm-mayer-brown-split-hong-kong-partnership-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>习近平的欧洲之行可能暴露西方对中国战略的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/xis-trip-europe-may-lay-bare-wests-divisions-over-china-strategy-2024-05-02/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平下周将五年来首次访问欧洲，这次访问可能会暴露欧洲在与北京的贸易问题上的分歧，以及欧洲大陆如何将自己定位为美国和中国之间的一极。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/xis-trip-europe-may-lay-bare-wests-divisions-over-china-strategy-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>五一假期中国旅游激增，但消费者仍保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-travel-surges-may-holiday-consumers-remain-wary-2024-05-02/</link><description>周三，即重大公众假期的第一天，中国各地的铁路和汽车出行激增，因为消费者仍然专注于在充满挑战的经济中降低开支。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-travel-surges-may-holiday-consumers-remain-wary-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能带动中国智能手机市场反弹，高通股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</link><description>高通公司股价周四上涨约 10% 至两年多高点，此前这家专注于智能手机的芯片制造商表示，在经历了多年的低迷之后，人工智能推动的需求出现反弹，尤其是在中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国一周内第二次“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-second-chinese-combat-patrol-week-2024-05-02/</link><description>台湾国防部周四表示，中国一周内第二次在台湾附近进行“联合战备巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-second-chinese-combat-patrol-week-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储缩减量化宽松安抚情绪，日元再次上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>韩国以朝鲜威胁为由提高外交警戒级别</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</link><description>韩国外交部周四提高了该地区五个外交机构的恐怖主义警戒级别，理由是有情报显示朝鲜可能试图伤害其官员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:21:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>经合组织上调全球增长前景 美国表现优于其他国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</link><description>经合组织周四表示，由于美国经济活动富有弹性，全球经济增长速度快于几个月前的预期，而通胀与央行目标的融合速度也快于预期，并上调了前景。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>Hugo Boss 股价因中国需求疲软和美国不确定性而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-q1-operating-profit-beats-expectations-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，Hugo Boss 股价下跌近 10%，触及 2022 年以来的最低水平，此前该高端服装品牌表示中国需求疲软，且对总统大选前的美国消费者信心感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:46:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-q1-operating-profit-beats-expectations-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>安赛乐米塔尔在盈利超出预期后坚持需求增长预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</link><description>全球第二大钢铁制造商安赛乐米塔尔周四公布第一季度财报，好于分析师预期，并重申今年中国以外全球钢铁需求将增长3-4%的预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员敦促中俄宣布只有人类而非人工智能控制核武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，一名美国高级官员敦促中国和俄罗斯效仿美国和其他国家的声明，即只有人类而非人工智能才能做出部署核武器的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰维持香港最优惠贷款利率于5.875%不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link><description>汇丰控股周四表示，在香港事实上的央行维持通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率不变，追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定后，该公司已将香港最优惠贷款利率维持在5.875%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行利润超出预期，费用收入增加抵消了信贷损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link><description>渣打银行周四第一季度税前利润超出预期，增长 5.5%，其交易和财富业务收入的激增足以弥补额外的信贷损失。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>